Package: pmon-update
Depends: linux-base, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: flash-kernel
Architecture: all
Description: pmon menu update
 Automatically create boot.cfg boot menu for pmon bootloader. Boot menu
 entries are automatically created for every kernel package when they are
 installed.
